<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/success.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Gothic:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>나눔마트 주문서</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="banner"></div>
            <h3>나눔마트 주문확인</h3>
            <div class="order_list">
                <p>
                    주문내역을 확인해주세요.<br>
                    주문 후 무통장입금계좌로 입금 부탁드립니다. 배송은 입금확인 후 진행됩니다.
                </p>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <td>주문자명</td>
                            <td class="name"><%-name%></td>
                            <td>전화번호</td>
                            <td class="phone"><%-phone%></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>수취인명</td>
                            <td class="pick_name"><%-pickName%></td>
                            <td>전화번호</td>
                            <td class="pick_phone"><%-pickPhone%></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>주소</td>
                            <td class="address" colspan="3"><%-address%></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>주문내용</td>
                            <td class="name" colspan="3"><textarea class="product" readonly><%-product%></textarea></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="4" style="text-align:center;">무통장입금 계좌</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>예금주</td>
                            <td class="bank_name">김우진</td>
                            <td>계좌번호</td>
                            <td class="bank_number">농협 302-0898-6017-31</td>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                </table>
                <a href="/">확인</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>